.DT
mail
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
mail

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
mail -  This is the main mail function.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int mail(string str,
string sub)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - 0 or "" for no default address
%^BOLD%^sub%^RESET%^ - the default subject

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/mail_track.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is the main mail function.  It tries to start up a mailer with
the default address and subject.  If there is no default address then
the mailer uses its menu mode, otherwise it sends one mail and then
leaves.
.EP

